{"tid":135243,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"隻貓一食罐頭就嘔","createTime":"2017-02-26T07:58:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T07:01:34.000Z","uid":69512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"97347f1c8310c27fb3ff7c46291f603536211bca","tid":135243,"uid":69512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T07:58:24.000Z","msg":"早排食罐頭都冇問題，食乾糧又唔會嘔，但唔知點解呢排一比罐頭佢食轉頭就嘔返曬岀黎，上網睇過話可能因為佢食得太快/腸胃有事，同埋啲屎又比以前軟左，有冇巴打隻貓都試過咁樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09cf86946db2f209cebe363aaee923137b70ba56","tid":135243,"uid":66669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T08:12:14.000Z","msg":"一樣情況 轉左乾糧長有，隔日罐就冇事"},{"pid":"a9d382dbbb792cf2178161ff8625ce36b87a3d33","tid":135243,"uid":60238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T10:08:39.000Z","msg":"食得太快姐<br />\n你試下一罐分開俾佢食啦"},{"pid":"57e99338bd65c4b4ef79fdc857bf56827bc57633","tid":135243,"uid":3180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T10:10:37.000Z","msg":"食返乾糧啦，罐罐都係唔好食咁密<br />\n依家食wellness core呢幾日啲屎終於靚返"},{"pid":"440341aaa4a23cafb00621a2fbdd4844b11bde2f","tid":135243,"uid":69512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T10:58:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食返乾糧啦，罐罐都係唔好食咁密<br />\n依家食wellness core呢幾日啲屎終於靚返</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n 我都係wellness core<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁我都係再觀察下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"473a91c0da31f1bc220326663150dac099437c63","tid":135243,"uid":69512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T11:00:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食得太快姐<br />\n你試下一罐分開俾佢食啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我已經係分開左架喇，但佢都係嘔，所以先驚係腸胃問題，諗住買益生菌試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3b7f2006b08f8dcb226d0153f00638c6bc6e846","tid":135243,"uid":69512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T11:42:47.000Z","msg":"推一推先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8454bde6b5d467aa5f0e5841d56f0b6e9bb46d27","tid":135243,"uid":35095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T12:33:58.000Z","msg":"我隻貓貓都係咁<br />\n又係食Wellness core 嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我觀察到有幾個可能原因：<br />\n- 每餐之間相隔太耐 （試下縮短每餐之間既時間，餵D小食咁）<br />\n- 罐頭有對貓貓腸胃敏感既成份 (轉糧 / 轉口味，雞肉同魚比較穩陣)<br />\n- 食得太快  (一餐分開兩至三碗，等佢食慢D)<br />\n<br />\n同埋 Wellness 質地好似太硬，我而家轉左餵instinct <br />\n同埋留意返以上幾點，已經有好大改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ae143748fd7cf84a7f2af246d3bff3dab7411b","tid":135243,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T12:36:38.000Z","msg":"餵開咩罐？好少聽貓食罐嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無加水同加得多唔多？<br />\n一食完有無即刻喪跑？"},{"pid":"c6c7a3ab03e1c22e3b358ea290cafbf481a8dab0","tid":135243,"uid":69512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T13:56:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>餵開咩罐？好少聽貓食罐嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無加水同加得多唔多？<br />\n一食完有無即刻喪跑？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔記得點串個名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 放工返去睇返先<br />\n無加水<br />\n成日跑同跳上跳落"},{"pid":"758dd8d276dd6821a1cc2309b4362587e67bd6e7","tid":135243,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T07:01:34.000Z","msg":"我果隻一食鍚紙袋果種濕糧就嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}